      "text": "Append only file\n    log every write operation persisted by server. These logs can be used at server startup to reconstructed dataset. \nHow it works \n    When redis is finished executing a  write command it will append the command at the end of the buffer of the server  \nin porotocal  format .\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Append only file\n    log every write operation persisted by server. These logs can be used at server startup to reconstructed dataset. \nHow it works \n    When redis is finished executing a  write command it will append the command at the end of the buffer of the server  \nin porotocal  format .\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1S7BEH2kOGL8f8jfPbSgn",
